  "description": "A [journal entry](../terms/journal.md) records a single transaction in the books using [double-entry bookkeeping](../terms/double-entry-bookkeeping.md). Every entry has a date, a description, and at least one [debit and one credit](../terms/debit-and-credit.md) that are equal in total.",
